&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Motional’s Las Vegas office is located less than 10 miles from the Las Vegas strip at 730 E Pilot Road and is home to one of the largest fleets of self-driving vehicles. The city’s grid system of roads and being one of America’s “smart cities” allows for extensive research and development testing.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mission Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated AV Test Engineer&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;to join our Team. In this strong intermediate level role, you will take full ownership of assigned tasks within defined test execution procedures and support the broader Test Engineering team in validating sophisticated autonomous systems. Working under the guidance of senior engineers, you will ensure our vehicles and systems are mission-ready through rigorous readiness checks, real-time monitoring, and low-level subsystem validation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
