&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Test Planning initiatives -&lt;/strong&gt; Define the test strategy, scope, resources, and timelines for new feature releases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End Test Case Development - &lt;/strong&gt;Design, write, and maintain detailed, reusable test cases and test suites that map directly to functional requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross teams to identify edge cases and ensure comprehensive test coverage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Test Execution &amp;amp; Readiness:&lt;/strong&gt; Take full ownership of assigned tasks within defined test procedures, including specific checklist items and system monitoring. Perform all pre- and post-test readiness checks completely, accurately, and on time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up, configure, and operate AB Dynamics systems (GST, Launchpad), including target preparation and robot operation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute structured scenario-based testing using track infrastructure and robotic platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subsystem Validation:&lt;/strong&gt; Execute and support fault injection and low-level control testing for critical subsystems, including actuator-level behavior (throttle, brake, steering) against expected control responses and safety constraints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Monitoring:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide timely and accurate real-time monitoring of assigned system statuses during testing to ensure safe and successful execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Execute basic configuration and setup of instrumentation and telemetry. Assist in on-vehicle and off-vehicle tests focusing on critical components such as control systems and perception.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize Vector tools (CANalyzer/CANoe) for live debugging, signal tracing, and post-test analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documentation &amp;amp; Triage:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain accurate, organized, and complete logs of all test activities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze vehicle logs (CAN, telemetry, system logs) to identify anomalies and support root cause analysis (RCA).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate directly with developers to reproduce issues and validate fixes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Issue Escalation:&lt;/strong&gt; Promptly and clearly escalate all anomalies or issues to a senior engineer immediately upon detection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simulation Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Support testing within virtual environments, including Software-in-the-Loop (SIL) and Hardware-in-the-Loop (HIL) platforms.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
