&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end commercial fleet performance across all active markets, including safety, reliability, utilization, and service delivery metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and drive KPIs such as fleet availability, autonomous miles, incident rates, MTTR (mean time to resolution), and SLA adherence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate operational data into actionable insights to continuously improve fleet efficiency, uptime, and customer experience.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
