&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and standardize operations across multiple geographies, ensuring consistency in execution while adapting to local Operational Design Domains (ODDs).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop scalable operating models that support expansion of fully driverless deployments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure operational readiness for new market launches, including staffing models, infrastructure, and regulatory alignment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Command Center &amp;amp; Incident Management Oversight:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide executive oversight of real-time fleet command and control functions, including incident response, escalation protocols, and non-nominal event management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure robust incident command structures are in place to rapidly contain risk and maintain public trust during high-severity events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive post-incident review processes to identify root causes and implement systemic corrective actions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Integration:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the senior operational liaison across Engineering, Safety, Product, Mapping, and Commercial teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align fleet operations with system capabilities, product roadmap, and safety frameworks to ensure cohesive execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Commercial and Business Development teams to support partner success and contractual performance obligations.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
