&lt;li&gt;Work with large-scale internal datasets to demonstrate the effectiveness of your research&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with different teams to deploy your research results into the autonomous vehicles&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Publish the research results in papers and patents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
